The following parts of internal/vips are adapted from imgproxy's vips package:

  - The streaming input source: the SharpgoSource VipsSource subclass backed by
    a runtime/cgo.Handle (internal/vips/source.go and the "streaming input
    source" section of internal/vips/bridge.c), from imgproxy's
    vips/source.{c,h,go}.
  - The sRGB ICC-profile fingerprint sharpgo_icc_is_srgb in
    internal/vips/bridge.c, from imgproxy's vips_icc_is_srgb_iec61966.

